highlights.text: Justin Bieber has the most spots on Top Songs Norway. “DAISIES” is the highest at #4.
“Die With A Smile” by Lady Gaga and Bruno Mars has been on Top Songs Norway the longest, at 330 days straight.
“DAISIES” by Justin Bieber is the highest new entry on Top Songs Norway at #4.
“What Did I Miss?” by Drake is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Norway, up 78 spots at #50.
